<br>
Perhaps you are using pure stats jewellery/accessories with no AC on them?<br>
<br>
For fingers get the 6ac 65hp Rings. they're relatively inexpensive these days [almost at cost anyway].<br>
<br>
For Earring, you might want to explore a Cougar Claw Earring, Vah Shir Claw Earring, or if money is not a problem, then Earring of the Solstice.<br>
<br>
Basically at L45, having 852ac is really not too shabby. With buffs etc, you should reach close to 1k anyway.<br>
<br>
Personal recommendation would be to get your levels up. Higher levels equate to being able to mitigate more damage from higher level mobs, which also equate to access to better loot/items, which then equate to increased ease in obtaining desired AC/stats.<br>
<br>
